            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>drained linguine</strong>&nbsp;with the reserved <strong>starchy pasta water&nbsp;</strong>and cook until the liquid thickens slightly and the <strong>tomatoes</strong> are starting to break down</p>",
